<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl py-10 space-y-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">What Enliterator Does</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-700">
    Enliterator transforms datasets into Enliterated Knowledge Navigators (EKNs)—long‑lived, rights‑aware companions that you can converse with, explore visually, and grow over time.
  </p>

  <section class="space-y-3">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Pipeline (Stages 1–8)</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Intake</strong>: Discover, hash, and partition files into IngestItems.</li>
      <li><strong>Rights & Provenance</strong>: Attach consent, license, ownership, publishability, and training eligibility.</li>
      <li><strong>Lexicon Bootstrap</strong>: Extract canonical terms and surface forms using OpenAI Structured Outputs.</li>
      <li><strong>Pool Filling</strong>: Populate the Ten Pool Canon (Idea, Manifest, Experience, Relational, Evolutionary, Practical, Emanation, …).</li>
      <li><strong>Graph Assembly</strong>: Build a Neo4j knowledge graph with constraints, indexes, and rich repr_text.</li>
      <li><strong>Representations & Retrieval</strong>: Generate embeddings directly in Neo4j (GenAI), enable semantic/hybrid search.</li>
      <li><strong>Literacy Scoring</strong>: Assess coverage, maturity, and gaps with actionable recommendations.</li>
      <li><strong>Deliverables</strong>: Export graph dumps, prompt packs, evaluation bundles, and multi‑format outputs.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-3">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Knowledge Navigators (EKNs)</h2>
    <p>
      Each EKN maintains identity, accumulates knowledge across batches, and powers a conversational interface (the Knowledge Navigator UI). The Meta‑Enliterator is an EKN that helps create other EKNs.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-3">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">What makes it different?</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Rights‑aware from ingest to answer synthesis.</li>
      <li>Transparent modeling via the Ten Pool Canon.</li>
      <li>Neo4j graph + vector search for structure and meaning.</li>
      <li>Structured Outputs for deterministic extraction.</li>
      <li>Evaluation bundles and scoring to ensure quality.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Highlights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <% (@features || [
        "Zero‑touch pipeline from intake to deliverables",
        "Rights‑aware processing with provenance throughout",
        "Ten Pool Canon modeling (Idea, Manifest, Experience, …)",
        "Neo4j knowledge graph with vector search (GenAI)",
        "OpenAI Structured Outputs for extraction",
        "Enliteracy scoring, gaps, and maturity assessment",
        "Autogenerated deliverables and prompt packs",
        "EKNs for persistent, conversational exploration"
      ]).each do |f| %>
        <li><%= f %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <div class="mt-6">
    <a href="/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Go to the Navigator</a>
  </div>
</div>
